  "description_long": "Habitat For Humanity Of Kansas City is a HUD-approved housing counseling agency in Kansas City, MO. As a federally approved organization, they provide free or low-cost counseling on housing, mortgage, and credit issues. Services include Default/Foreclosure Counseling, Home Improvement/Rehabilitation, Non-Delinquency Post-Purchase Counseling, Pre-Purchase Homebuyer Education. HUD-approved agencies must meet federal standards for counselor training and service quality.",
